articles.title: San Jose Amateur Astronomers to Screen Space Film
articles.summary: The San Jose Amateur Astronomers will screen a space film on Feb. 6, focusing on America's Project Mercury mission to put a man in space.

articles.title: Sally Elizabeth Krumm Engaged to James Stanley Styczynski
articles.summary: Sally Elizabeth Krumm announces her engagement to James Stanley Styczynski at a dinner party in Cupertino. The prospective groom is stationed at Travis Air Force Base as a future control system mechanic.
